snippet.title: Apocalypse Cow - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Apocalypse Cow is a cinematic arcade adventure set in a broken digital universe. Coming to Xbox One and PC in 2018.

Wishlist now on Steam!: http://store.steampowered.com/app/592380/Apocalypse_Cow

An adorably psychotic girl with the power to rupture time, travels across GameWorlds to find a missing robot. It's a journey that will teach her the true meaning of friendship and explosions.
 
http://ApocalypseCowGame.com
